data.description: Captivating custom residence on a 2.3-acre estate featuring a creek & a tranquil pond adorned with a water feature. Summer is for basking in the sparkling pool. The outdoor living area is an entertainer's delight, with a grill, fire pit, & plenty of storage. Inside discover a true masterpiece, with the open floor plan that integrates stunning wood floors and impeccable ceiling treatments. The gourmet kitchen is a haven for culinary enthusiasts. Enjoy movie nights in the media room, pool in the game room, or use the game room as a 4th bed as it comes with its own full bath. The elegant study is perfect, adorned with ample wood bookshelves and built-ins. And when it's time to retire, the master sanctuary beckons, boasting an oversized bath, a walk-in shower, and an expansive walk-in closet. Don't forget the storm shelter in the garage, an attic lift for easy access to the foam-insulated attic, and a large 3-car garage.
